<p>Hello {{{Recipient.Name}}},</p>

<p>Welcome on board! We’re thrilled to have you join Serpent.</p>

<p>To activate your plan, just follow these quick steps:</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Create Your Account</strong></p>
    <p>Sign up using this [link] - be sure to use your work email: {{{Recipient.Email}}}</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Complete Your Payment</strong></p>
    <p>Use the same email to complete your custom plan payment [here].</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Your Plan Includes:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>X minutes/month</strong> of automation</li>
  <li><strong>$X/month</strong> - pricing tailored to your needs</li>
  <li>Includes access to:
    <ul>
      <li>Automated Deployments.</li>
      <li>Real-Time Monitoring.</li>
      <li>Unlimited Projects.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>Want a smooth onboarding? You can book a <strong>free walkthrough session</strong> <a href="https://outlook.office365.com/book/serpentmeetings@tekunda.com/">here</a> to get the most out of Serpent from day one.</p>

<p>If you have any questions at all, just reply to this email - we’re here for you.</p>

<p>
Best regards,<br />
Serpent Team <strong>|</strong> Tekunda<br />
